ltl2rabin

Class SlaveFromFormulaFactory

  • Object
    • ltl2rabin.AutomatonFactory<F,A,L>
      • ltl2rabin.RabinAutomatonFactory<Formula,List<MojmirAutomaton.State<PropEquivalenceClass,Set<String>>>,Set<String>>
        • ltl2rabin.SlaveFromFormulaFactory

  • public class SlaveFromFormulaFactory
extends RabinAutomatonFactory<Formula,List<MojmirAutomaton.State<PropEquivalenceClass,Set<String>>>,Set<String>>
    A SlaveFromFormulaFactory can create a Slave from an LTL object, using its alphabet. Once constructed, every generated automaton will be put into a cache, so constructing a Slave several times from the same formula will be efficient.
